<i>adjective</i>: 한심하다 [한심하다], 한심스럽다 [한심스럽따], 안쓰럽다 [안쓰럽따], 갸륵하다 [갸ː르카다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>한심하다 [한심하다]</dt><br>
<dd>pathetic; pitiable; deplorable</dd><br>
<dd>정도에 너무 지나치거나 모자라서 딱하거나 어이없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Looking pitiable or making another dumbfounded because one goes far beyond a certain limit or falls short of his/her expectation.</dd><br>
<dt>한심스럽다 [한심스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>pathetic; pitiable; deplorable</dd><br>
<dd>정도에 너무 지나치거나 모자라서 딱하거나 어이없는 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Looking pitiable or making another dumbfounded because one goes far beyond a certain limit or falls short of his/her expectation.</dd><br>
<dt>안쓰럽다 [안쓰럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. feeling sorry</dd><br>
<dd>자기보다 어리거나 약한 사람에게 도움을 받고 폐를 끼쳐 미안하고 딱하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling uneasy and sorry about getting help from and imposing on someone who is younger or weaker.</dd><br>
<dd>2. feeling bad; pitiable; pathetic</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 처지나 형편이 딱하고 불쌍하여 마음이 좋지 않다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling upset because someone's situation or circumstances are bad and pitiful.</dd><br>
<dt>갸륵하다 [갸ː르카다]</dt><br>
<dd>unfortunate; pitiable; pathetic</dd><br>
<dd>처지가 안 되고 불쌍하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's situation being pitiful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>